# Bind Mount Example

## Q13: Mount Host Directory

Linux / Mac:

```bash
docker run -it -v $(pwd):/workspace ubuntu bash
```

Windows PowerShell:

```bash
docker run -it -v ${PWD}:/workspace ubuntu bash
```

