# Docker Image Management

## Q14: List and Delete Images

```bash
docker images
docker rmi image_id
docker image prune
```

---

## Q15: Build Custom Image

Example Dockerfile:

```Dockerfile
FROM ubuntu:20.04

RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y nginx

EXPOSE 80

CMD ["nginx","-g","daemon off;"]
```

Build image:

```bash
docker build -t mynginx:v1 .
```

Run container:

```bash
docker run -d -p 8080:80 mynginx:v1
```

